subSubSection.paragraph:
Illustrations :— Saint-Hilaire (1824 : t. XV—two habitus drawings); Eichler (1872: t. 90, fig. II pro parte : habit illustrated on the left and flower parts 2, 2II, 4—as
Drosera intermedia
); Hamet (1907 : t. II, fig. 5—seed); Hoehne (1915 : t. 124, fig. 3—habit and details, as
D. communis var. alba
); Duno de Stefano et al. (2001: 11, fig. 2—habit and details); Rivadavia (2003: 89, figs. 4.2A-E, 4.1F, G—habit and details).
